# vhs Layer 4 — Live K-EXAONE Korean greeting chat.
Output specs/integration-verification/frames/vhs-03-chat.gif
Output specs/integration-verification/frames/vhs-03-chat.txt
Output specs/integration-verification/frames/vhs-03-chat.ascii
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set Width 1600
Set Height 900
Set Theme "TokyoNightStorm"
Hide
Type "cd /Users/um-yunsang/KOSMOS/tui && KOSMOS_ONBOARDING_AUTO_COMPLETE=1 bun run tui"
Enter
Sleep 5s
Show
Screenshot specs/integration-verification/frames/vhs-03-keyframe-1-boot.png
Sleep 500ms
Type "안녕하세요"
Sleep 1s
Screenshot specs/integration-verification/frames/vhs-03-keyframe-2-typed.png
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 8s
Screenshot specs/integration-verification/frames/vhs-03-keyframe-3-thinking.png
Sleep 12s
Screenshot specs/integration-verification/frames/vhs-03-keyframe-4-response.png
Sleep 500ms
Ctrl+C
Sleep 500ms
Ctrl+C
Sleep 1s
